     */
    func isExpired()  -> Bool
    
    /**
     * The issuer of the offer or refund.
     *
     * From [`Offer::issuer`] or [`Refund::issuer`].
     *
     * [`Offer::issuer`]: lightning::offers::offer::Offer::issuer
     * [`Refund::issuer`]: lightning::offers::refund::Refund::issuer
